<title>SOUTH AFRICA: WBH-Ovcon yr shr up, div increased.</title>
<headline>WBH-Ovcon yr shr up, div increased.</headline>
<dateline>JOHANNESBURG 1997-02-28</dateline>
<text>
<p>Half year ended December 31, 1996</p>
<p>			(million rand unless stated)</p>
